\begin{align*}
2ab &= 12\\
\Rightarrow\quad ab &= 6\\
\Rightarrow\quad a &= \frac{6}{b}\\

&= 8\left(\frac{6}{b}\right)\left(\frac{6}{b}\right)b^2\\
&= 48\left(\frac{6}{b}\right)\\
&= 288\\
\end{align*}
So $8a^2b^2 = 288$.
